    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, providing direct tactile feedback. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including VANOS timing adjustment and rear subframe reinforcement to manage torsional stress. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and a variable M differential lock ensuring precise power delivery. A purist\u2019s spec focused on drivetrain excellence and linear performance.",
